bout the Apple iWatch?<\/span><br \/>\nEveryone\u2019s certain that Apple will launch the two iPhone 6 models at the event \u2013 but there could be some more surprises also. According to the rumors, we assume that the long-awaited iWatch should also debut at Apple\u2019s Sept. 9 event. iWatch would beat the competing fitness bands and help in health tracking. The fans have been expecting fitness tracking features from iWatch \u2013 collect data on the user\u2019s heart rate, motion and much more.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: large;\">The rumor about Apple iPad Air 2:<\/span><br \/>\niPad Air 2 is also rumored to hit the stage at the event. The device would be having the same fast A8 processor as in iPhone 6. Another rumored feature includes a Touch ID sensor for security and a new gold color option too.<br \/>\n&nbsp;<br \/>\nNothing\u2019s yet certain, but Apple would unveil the secret soon. Let\u2019s wait to see what features does the most-awaited iPhone 6 has for us!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The most awaited Apple iPhone 6 is believed to be the biggest device launch event this year. The next-generation iPhone would have 4.7&#8243; and 5.5&#8243; screens along with several added features that would make iPhone 6 a preferred choice of users and developers across the globe. Apple is also gearing up to make their first [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"ngg_post_thumbnail":0},"categories":[1170],"tags":[],"acf":{"show_blog_end":"no","add_blog_end":"","display_hellobar":false,"add_hellobar":"","add_hellobar_link":"","bottom_cta_text":"","bottom_cta_link":"","featured_posts":["no"],"add_text":"","text_color":"#000000","top_cta_text":"","top_cta_link":""},"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v20.6 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>The trio \u201